{
  "stem": "3653.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When you look back on those early days of being a young boy, what stands out the most?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a strong man, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was always in the business, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was the business man from the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I enjoyed this, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't see-- I didn't see, because they died before, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, I remember, like-- like you know, through a sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I can't even recognize, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lost 70 people from my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, like weddings, you know, together, like, in the synagogue, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, we were in good times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Europe, it was not like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody separate, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Passover was a-- was a holiday, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to make wine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father bought grapes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, and lady squeezes this in a bottle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it has to stay two weeks, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] wine, matzohs, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a nice, nice Passover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, later in the end it was already machines that they make matzohs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we bake by hand, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cause you know, if you bake by hand, it's more kosher, like they say, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sisters, the father, the mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a big family, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, Passover, [INAUDIBLE], Rosh Hashanah, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, [INAUDIBLE] they used to get drunk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used the dance in the streets with the Torahs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if somebody got married, they make the hoop and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody touched us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they go around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They talk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They walk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes a kiss.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they're starting to change when Hitler came to power, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
